        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="108" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>When you close the entries for the previous fiscal year, you can create several lines by setting the <bpt id="p1">**</bpt>Type<ept id="p1">**</ept> field to <bpt id="p2">**</bpt>Opening<ept id="p2">**</ept>.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="109" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>This allows special opening entries for the current fiscal year to be posted.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="110" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>You can make adjustments to the opening sheet for the fiscal year on the <bpt id="p1">**</bpt>Opening sheets<ept id="p1">**</ept> page.</source>
        </trans-unit>
