          <source>To create a new <bpt id="p1">**</bpt>Opening sheet,<ept id="p1">**</ept> click <bpt id="p2">**</bpt>New<ept id="p2">**</ept> on the <bpt id="p3">**</bpt>Opening sheets<ept id="p3">**</ept> page, and specify the following.</source>
